data.description:
Back on the Market! Open floor plan, Corner Lot Single floor Home on a Cul-de-sac street.  Brand new LVP flooring in Living room and hallways and brand-new carpet in all bedrooms. 
New fresh paint inside and outside.  Master Bathroom was recently remodeled.  Newer roof (just replaced in 2020).  Brand new water heater installed in 2023.  Backyard is fully fenced in.
